
[Open Broadcaster Software]
Installare OBS su Ubuntu 18.04 LTS

1) xserver-xorg version 1.18.4 or newer is recommended
	per vedere se c'e' e quale versione: dpkg -l |grep xserver-xorg-core

2) FFmpeg is required
	per vedere se c'e': 
		
		dpkg -l |grep ffmpeg

		ffmpeg -version



	per installarlo:
		sudo apt-get update
		sudo apt-get install ffmpeg

In caso di errore dovuto al package "jitsi" 
	service jitsi-videobridge stop
	sudo apt-get purge jigasi jitsi-meet jitsi-meet-web-config jitsi-meet-prosody jitsi-meet-turnserver jitsi-meet-web jicofo jitsi-videobridge
	sudo apt-get purge jigasi jitsi-meet jitsi-meet-web-config jitsi-meet-prosody jitsi-meet-web jicofo jitsi-videobridge
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install ffmpeg
	ffmeg -version
	


3) installa OBS 
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:obsproject/obs-studio
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install obs-studio


	
